    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-24">
      <!-- Desktop Sticky Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 methodology-sidebar">
        <div class="hidden lg:block lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          <h3
            id="nav-methodology"
            class="methodology-nav-item font-black text-[60px] leading-[1.1] mb-2 transition-opacity duration-300"
            data-target="section-methodology"
          >
            Methodology
          </h3>
          <h3
            id="nav-output"
            class="methodology-nav-item font-black text-[60px] leading-[1.1] opacity-30 transition-opacity duration-300"
            data-target="section-output"
          >
            Output
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scrolling Content -->
      <div class="lg:w-2/3">
        <!-- Methodology Content -->
        <div
          id="section-methodology"
          class="methodology-section mb-24 lg:mb-40"
        >
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- M1 with Slider -->
            <div class="relative methodology-card" data-card="m1">
              <div
                class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-pink to-transparent"
              >
              </div>
              <div class="pl-6">
                <h4 class="font-black text-4xl lg:text-[60px] mb-4">Ⓜ➀</h4>
                <p
                  class="text-lg lg:text-[25px] leading-[1.2] font-semibold mb-4"
                >
                  "critical training in empathetic relational imagination"
                </p>
                <!-- Slides Container -->
                <div class="methodology-slides" data-slides="m1">
                  <div class="methodology-slide active" data-slide="0">
                    <p
                      class="text-sm lg:text-[18px] leading-[1.4] font-semibold opacity-80"
                    >
                      1. training through gestures, dances, music coming from
                      mediterranean ancestral "continuum" community (open to
                      other convenings from more than design radical pedagogies
                      and epistemologies)
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="methodology-slide" data-slide="1">
                    <p
                      class="text-sm lg:text-[18px] leading-[1.4] font-semibold opacity-80"
                    >
                      2. doing means following the teachings of an established
                      mentor from the community, happening mostly in residential
                      workshops with transfer of embodied knowledge
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="methodology-slide" data-slide="2">
                    <p
                      class="text-sm lg:text-[18px] leading-[1.4] font-semibold opacity-80"
                    >
                      3. I'll keep a multimedia diary extended with direct
                      contributions from the mentors and other participants
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="methodology-slide" data-slide="3">
                    <p
                      class="text-sm lg:text-[18px] leading-[1.4] font-semibold opacity-80"
                    >
                      4. I'll study with psychologists and neuroscientists (who
                      work on group awareness and regulation) and start
                      developing a measuring system to be tested on myself and
                      the other participants
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
